dcterms:description: The WMT19 dataset is used for machine translation tasks, specifically for translating English documents into Chinese. It consists of individual sentences that are concatenated to recover document structures.

dcterms:description: PARABANK is a large-scale English paraphrase dataset constructed with a Czech-English neural machine translation system. It is used for paraphrase identification tasks.
dcterms:title: PARABANK

dcterms:description: WikiText-103 is a collection of Wikipedia articles used for language modeling tasks. It provides a rich source of text data for training and evaluating language models.
